The pose_landmarker_lite.task file is the MediaPipe Pose Landmarker model (~4MB).

Download from: https://storage.googleapis.com/mediapipe-models/pose_landmarker/pose_landmarker_lite/float16/latest/pose_landmarker_lite.task

Place the downloaded file here as: pose_landmarker_lite.task

This file is not committed to git due to its size. It will be bundled into the
Android app via the assets directory.
